    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="border border-wood-100 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button onclick="toggleAccordion(0)" class="w-full text-left px-6 py-4 bg-wood-50 hover:bg-wood-100 font-semibold text-wood-300 flex justify-between items-center">
          <span>地板安裝需要多長時間？</span>
          <span class="text-2xl">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="accordion-content px-6 py-0">
          <p class="text-wood-400 py-4">一般住宅項目約需2-5個工作天，視乎面積大小及地板類型。我們會在報價時提供準確時間表。</p>
